flowchart LR
  %% HackTrap AI Threat Monitor - Component Diagram

  subgraph Client[Frontend (Vite App)]
    UI[index.html + styles.css\nScrollable dashboard layout]
    State[main.js\nState + render pipeline]
    Map[Leaflet map\nGlobal marker visualization]
    SocketClient[Socket.IO client\nnew_event stream]
    RestClient[Fetch client\nPolling + snapshots]
  end

  subgraph API[Backend (Node.js + Express + Socket.IO)]
    Server[server.js\nHTTP + WebSocket orchestration]
    Generator[generator.js\nSession-based synthetic event generation]
    Analyzer[analyzer.js\nThreat + intent + stage + prediction]
    Profiles[profiles.js\nIP attacker profile store]
    Memory[(In-memory buffers\nEvents + profile state)]
  end

  UI --> State
  State --> Map
  State --> SocketClient
  State --> RestClient

  SocketClient <-->|WebSocket: new_event| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/events| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/system-status| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/attackers| Server
  RestClient <-->|REST: /api/attackers/:ip| Server

  Server --> Generator
  Generator --> Analyzer
  Analyzer --> Profiles

  Generator --> Memory
  Analyzer --> Memory
  Profiles --> Memory
  Server --> Memory
